channel.title: Need help!@ 100% unanswered!
channel.description: Ok so i am using the zombie-scape source. If you try and wear items (even if u have stat requirements) it wont let you. It's not that you dont have requirements met but its just weird that u cant wear. The coder of the server did say in his post in download section he broke the cache and u have to code in the items urself but how do you do that? please help
